Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.33,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Still, my brother will be happy that you've come.}Dù sao thì, Onii-chan rất vui khi cậu qua đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh?! H-he'll be happy?}Hể?! A-Anh ấy vui à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yup! He said that making food\Nfor a Christmas party makes it extra special.}Ừm! Anh ấy sẽ nấu một bữa\N đặc biệt cho dịp Giáng sinh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.17,0:08:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{Huh? I-I guess so, yes.}C-Cũng đúng nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{I-I'm happy too.}M-Mình vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{I haven't given Taihei a present since his birthday.}Ngoài dịp sinh nhật, mình \Nchưa từng tặng quà cho Onii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{There's so much I can't thank him enough for...}Có nhiều thứ mà mình vẫn chưa cảm ơn anh ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{You got my brother a present?!}Cậu đã .. chuẩn bị quà ... cho Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{Yes! And there's one for you as well.}Ừm! Và cậu cũng có nữa, Umaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.21,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{O-oh, thank you!}C-Cảm ơn cậu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{What will YOU be giving your brother?}Cậu định tặng Onii-san cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{I thought maybe you and I\Ncould buy him a present together.}Mình đã nghĩ là chúng ta có thể \Ncùng đi mua quà cho Onii-chan đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, well, if you don't mind.}Ra là vậy. Mình xin lỗi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{I tried thinking of what to give him, but it was so hard...}Mình đã cố nghĩ xem có thể tặng anh ấy \Ncái gì, nhưng khó khăn quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{What did you get for him?}Ebina tặng cái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{U-um, well...}À-À thì ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{Ah! I'm sure he'll like that!}Mình nghĩ anh ấy sẽ rất vui vì nó đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.25,0:09:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hmm, but what should I get him?}Nên tặng anh ấy cái gì đây?
