Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you very much!}Cảm ơn quý khách!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{Thank you, Umaru. So, I guess it's my turn.}Cảm ơn cậu, Umaru. Đến lượt mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{This is your present!}Quà của cậu nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You brought it with you? Thank you!}Cậu mang theo nó à? Cảm ơn nhiều!
