Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{L-look, it was a coincidence\Nhe came here in the first place.} T-Thôi nào, chỉ là tình cờ qua chơi thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{But you both go to the same school, don't you?} Onee-chan, Onii-chan \N học cùng trường với chị phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh, no. She's being really pushy today!} {\i1}Không được rồi. \N Hôm nay con bé làm sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.29,0:13:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{He's at the top of his class?} Onii-chan cũng đứng đầu lớp luôn ạ?
